lli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1769\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/501317\">21 cl. 3 no. 7\u003C/ref>\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/SPTB56H3\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Castelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1784\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/501727\">24 cl. 3 no. 8\u003C/ref>\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/7PSFHSUH\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Cavallaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1939\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>26\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3F3DEGND\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002330\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002330\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Misuraca\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1962\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>33\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/ZRGBK6DY\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002331\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002331\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                  